room_title: Escape room "Escape Trump's America" by Tales From The Cryptex in Sacramento
room_description:
This room offers all Americans and immigrants (for a limited time only) the opportunity to escape to The Great White North. Escapers can experience the joys of planning a move to Canada at a fraction of the cost of doing the real thing. Find clues, solve riddles and piece together loosely themed puzzles to collect the items needed to make your move.
Support Trump? No Problem! Trump supporters can still have fun solving puzzles in the Escape Trump's America room.
